<p>
  Another use for quicksort if you want to find all y's for x. For example, what are all the songs of Queen, or what
  are all the movies Tarantino made? Additionally, you can create topics where you add constraints about the content
  that you want. For example: what are all the songs of Queen on grooveshark, or all the movies of Tarantino on
  thepiratebay.org, in english, and at least 720p ?
</p>


