I'm happy to see that you like it. Here is what you can do to help the project get bigger:
<ul>
  <li>
    Next time you look for something specific on the internet, create a topic. And as you find good links for it,
    add them to your own topic (it could be right away or later). You people will thank you by upvoting your
    topic and links, and you might also have people adding links you didn't know about.
  </li>
  <li>
    Whenever you find a very good piece of content, bookmark it in a folder called "List of useful". When this
    bookmark gets too big, submit all the links to quicksort on the page "List of usefull". Then you organize them
    into topics, (or let other people do that if you don't have time)
  </li>
